# 7. Amazon VPC

### Components

- VPC
- Public Subnet
- Private Subnet
- Internet Gateway
- Route Table
- Network ACL
- NAT Gateway
- Security Group

### Best Practice Architecture

```text
Internet
    │
Internet Gateway
    │
Public Subnet
    │
EC2 Instance
    │
Private Subnet
    │
RDS Database
```

### Why Keep RDS Private?

- Better security
- Prevent direct internet access
- Reduced attack surface
- Secure communication through EC2

